The World Council of Churches has held 10 Assemblies to date, starting with the founding assembly in 1948:&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.oikoumene.org/en/about-us/organizational-structure/assembly/since-1948 Timeline | | World Council of Churches]. Oikoumene.org. Retrieved 2014-01-15.&lt;/ref&gt;
