#[[Vancouver, British Columbia|Vancouver]], [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]] 24 July – 10 August 1983
#[[Canberra]], [[Australian Capital Territory|ACT]], [[Australia]], 7–21 February 1991&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.wcc-assembly.info/index.php?id=514 10th Assembly of the World Council of Churches — WCC 10th Assembly]. WCC-Assembly.info (2012-10-29). Retrieved on 2013-08-09.&lt;/ref&gt;
#[[Harare]], [[Zimbabwe]], 3–14 December 1998
#[[Porto Alegre]], [[Rio Grande do Sul]], [[Brazil]], 14–23 February 2006
#[[Busan]], [[South Korea]], 30 October – 8 November 2013

