Presidents of the current 10th Assembly are:&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.oikoumene.org/en/press-centre/news/assembly-elects-new-wcc-presidents Press Center | World Council of Churches]. Oikoumene.org. Retrieved on 2014-01-13.&lt;/ref&gt;
